---
title: Bring Home the Bacon Spaghetti with Tomatoes, Bell Pepper, Italian Cheese & Scallions
description: This rich, satisfying riff on the traditional Italian amatriciana sauce (the folks in the town of Amatrice say it must contain cured pork jowl, among other things, or it’s not the real deal) is made instead with smoky bacon, onion and bell pepper for sweet-savoryness. Tomatoes add brightness, and a creamy, rich Italian cheese blend + butter make for a full-bodied sauce that pairs perfectly with al dente spaghetti. Don’t tell Amatrice how divine it is!
